snippet.textDisplay: The best part of CS is that it has revived the long forgotten poetry and folk music. People like us who left country, still connect the whole family with our country through this kind of music. Our whole family including my 10 yrs old son and 14 yrs old daughter here in Toronto set together and watched/listened this song several times. This is an excellent composition and of course lyrics are mind blowing.  Natasha Baig ! You have simply nailed it. Should we expect few more songs from you in CS?
